org.apache.ambari.server.controller.internal

Class StackDefinedPropertyProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ambari.server.controller.internal.StackDefinedPropertyProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PropertyProvider

    public class StackDefinedPropertyProvider
extends Object
implements PropertyProvider
    This class analyzes a service's metrics to determine if additional metrics should be fetched. It's okay to maintain state here since these are done per-request.

                                       Request request,

                                throws SystemException
        Description copied from interface: PropertyProvider
        Populate the given set of resource with any properties that this property provider can provide and return a populated set of resources. The provider may drop resources from the original set if it determines that the don't meet the conditions of the predicate.
        Specified by:

        Parameters:
        resources - the resources to be populated
        request - the request object which defines the desired set of properties
        predicate - the predicate object which filters which resources are returned
        Returns:

        Throws:
